            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tomato haddock gnocchi</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>harissa & coriander butter</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
